Summary: Defines the properties for the AudioStreamWAV class, including audio data, format, loop settings, mix rate, stereo configuration, and tags.

Properties:
* data (PackedByteArray): The raw audio data. Default: PackedByteArray()
* format (Format): The audio format. Default: 0
* loop_begin (int): The starting point of the loop in samples. Default: 0
* loop_end (int): The ending point of the loop in samples. Default: 0
* loop_mode (LoopMode): The loop mode. Default: 0
* mix_rate (int): The mix rate (sample rate) of the audio in Hz. Default: 44100
* stereo (bool): Whether the audio is stereo. Default: false
* tags (Dictionary): A dictionary containing metadata tags. Default: {}
